文提到过的</li>\r\n</ul></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"拓展\">拓展</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>I beg your pardon</code> 请你原谅</li>\r\n<li><code>First you borrow, then you beg</code>\r\n（如果你浪费，）你首先借钱，然后乞讨要饭</li>\r\n<li><code>Spare a change</code> 舍弃一个零钱（给我）吧！</li>\r\n<li><code>A young idler(碌碌无为的人), an old beggar</code>\r\n少壮不努力，老大徒伤悲</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n","text":"新概念英语第二册-Lesson6 词汇 beggar 乞丐 乞求的人 food 食物 pocket 衣服口袋 call 拜访，光顾 打电话 call at sb 拜访某人 knock 敲门；打 kncok on/at the door meal 餐 beer 啤酒 表达 He a...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"NewConceptEnglish2","slug":"NewConceptEnglish2","count":8,"path":"api/tags/NewConceptEnglish2.json"},{"name":"English","slug":"English","count":8,"path":"api/tags/English.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%86%8C-lesson6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">新概念英语第二册-Lesson6</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AF%8D%E6%B1%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">词汇</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">表达</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">文章</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E7%82%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">语言点</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">名词的数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D%E4%BF%AE%E9%A5%B0%E8%AF%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">名词修饰词</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E